task.summary: Added For, While and Do-while into Repo
Continuing of Array of Objects and examples of the String class
Adding the a few more regex examples including string rules, email rules and password.
Adding more regex examples using the look ahead operator ?=

Adding method exercises a. Create a method that returns a random number from 1- (upper limit) i. Hint: Use the Math.random() method ii. upper limit should be an argument to the method b. Create a method that outputs all numbers divisible by 3 and 5 from a range i. Method should receive 1 argument (upper limit) ii. Lower limit is always 0 iii. Use print and not println c. Create a method that returns the sum of any array of integers i. Method should receive an integer's array as argument d. Create a method that returns the number of vowels in a string i. Method should receive any string as argument
Adding more info about overloading and static fields
